    "This could make these models more effective tools for medical education and assessment.",
    "Section 4: Applications of generative AI in orthopedic educationGenerative AI technologies have the potential to transform orthopedic education by enhancing learning methodologies, personalizing educational materials, and assisting in improving clinical skills and reasoning [54].",
