    "AI-powered clinical simulations would enable students to refine their reasoning, communication, and technical skills in a realistic, controlled setting.",
    "Furthermore, generative AI's integration with Virtual Reality can offer simulated surgical experiences, preparing trainees for complicated procedures through immersive, hands-on practice [56,57]."
